  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegan butter in a large pot over medium heat. ",
    "Add the onion and garlic and sauté until the onion is translucent. ",
    "Add the chicken bouillon powder and sauté for 1 minute. ",
    "Add the pickle juice and lemon juice and stir to combine. ",
    "Add the chicken breast and coconut milk and bring to a simmer. ",
    "Reduce heat to low and let cook for 15 minutes or until the chicken is cooked through. ",
    "Use an immersion blender to puree the soup until smooth. ",
    "Stir in the curry powder, salt, and black pepper. ",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped cilantro. ",
    "Adjust seasoning as needed. ",
    "Serve with steamed rice or noodles if desired. "
  ],
